{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775856784265,"sessionID":"ses_286b0173effehMzZXYWbZMW44j","part":{"id":"prt_d79500ef3001i1S4IZU0cCvoMU","messageID":"msg_d79500674001WsG5AqdLlGvuAr","sessionID":"ses_286b0173effehMzZXYWbZMW44j","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_a7cea5f63dd2443b9fa49f6e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-016/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-016/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Spec: AR-016 — PicoD 文件管理 API\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: This delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the PicoD file management API in `pkg/picod`.\n6: \n7: ## Base Specifications\n8: \n9: - **AR**: AR-016\n10: - **Module**: `pkg/picod`\n11: - **Language**: Go\n12: - **Size**: M\n13: - **Base Spec**: `deployment/client-go.md` (client-go library), `code-execution/spec.md`\n14: \n15: ---\n16: \n17: ## Background\n18: \n19: PicoD is an HTTP daemon that runs commands inside a configurable workspace jail, manages workspace files, and exposes a health endpoint with JWT (RSA)-protected APIs. This delta covers the file management API implementation in `pkg/picod`.\n20: \n21: ---\n22: \n23: ## Requirements\n24: \n25: ### AR-016-001: TBD\n26: \n27: ---\n28: \n29: ## References\n30: \n31: - Base spec: `deployment/client-go.md`\n32: - Design: `code-execution/design.md`\n33: - Spec: `code-execution/spec.md`\n34: - Module: `pkg/picod`\n35: - Related: AR-015 (PicoD 命令执行 API)\n\n(End of file - total 35 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Spec: AR-016 — PicoD 文件管理 API\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the PicoD file management API in `pkg/picod`.\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-016\n- **Module**: `pkg/picod`\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: M\n- **Base Spec**: `deployment/client-go.md` (client-go library), `code-execution/spec.md`\n\n---\n\n## Background\n\nPicoD is an HTTP daemon that runs commands inside a configurable workspace jail, manages workspace files, and exposes a health endpoint with JWT (RSA)-protected APIs. This delta covers the file management API implementation in `pkg/picod`.\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-016/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775856784246,"end":1775856784263}}}}
