{"type":"text","timestamp":1775856795359,"sessionID":"ses_286b0173effehMzZXYWbZMW44j","part":{"id":"prt_d795034d1001JKtqpA2nIELUv5","messageID":"msg_d79502115001rLmEpkdLpmCKFG","sessionID":"ses_286b0173effehMzZXYWbZMW44j","type":"text","text":"## AR-016 — PicoD 文件管理 API Archive Summary\n\n### Completed ✓\n- **Phase 1 Core Handlers**: UploadFileHandler, ListFilesHandler, DownloadFileHandler, Path sanitization\n- **Most Acceptance Criteria**: POST/GET endpoints, path traversal prevention, file mode handling, proper response formats\n\n### Deferred (未完成)\n- **DeleteFileHandler** — file/directory removal\n- **Phase 2**: Client-go integration (SharedInformerFactory, AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter listers)\n- **Phase 3**: Error handling standardization, logging integration\n- **Phase 4**: Unit tests and integration tests\n\n**Status**: Stage ST-1 (Spec Draft) — 核心文件操作已完成，client-go 集成和测试待后续完成。","time":{"start":1775856795354,"end":1775856795354}}}
